[{"videoWebUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@kenziecourtney7/video/7581909204273745183", "submittedVideoUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@kenziecourtney7/video/7581909204273745183", "input": "https://www.tiktok.com/@kenziecourtney7/video/7581909204273745183", "cid": "7601698662314853175", "createTime": 1769908422, "createTimeISO": "2026-02-01T01:13:42.000Z", "text": "They are complaining because these programs never allow you to OWN anything. When WiFi is down or you don’t have money for the subscription then how will you use it? With other consoles you at least have the OPTION to own or pay a subscription. Our Xbox, computer, and Wii allow downloadable subscriptions or ownership of games for when we don’t want YET ANOTHER SUBSCRIPTION we never own. Also when they stop supporting the nex playground which happens with ALL technology you won’t be able to play old games so your money just goes down the drain. All technology becomes obsolete but I can STILL play my old Nintendo 64, Xbox 360, and PlayStation games because I OWN them.", "diggCount": 6, "likedByAuthor": false, "pinnedByAuthor": false, "repliesToId": null, "replyCommentTotal": 4, "uid": "7547243785844540430", "uniqueId": "defiantdaisy", "avatarThumbnail": "https://p16-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tos-useast5-avt-0068-tx/ca1f8453fd6d98ab622469111eb360f0~tplv-tiktokx-cropcenter:100:100.jpg?dr=9640&refresh_token=f794fa99&x-expires=1775750400&x-signature=mGdzU0IoYheTxl7J5pleXKnJFK4%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=30310797&shcp=ff37627b&idc=useast5", "mentions": [], "detailedMentions": [], "text_zh": "他们抱怨是因为这些程序从来就不让你拥有东西。一旦没网了或者没钱续费了，那怎么用？其他游戏机至少可以选择拥有或者付费订阅。我们的 Xbox、电脑和 Wii 都支持下载订阅或购买游戏，这样我们就不需要再多一个我们永远不拥有的订阅。而且当他们停止支持那个新的游乐场，就像所有技术一样，你就没法玩老游戏了，钱就打了水漂。所有技术都会过时，但我仍然可以玩我的老款 Nintendo 64、Xbox 360 和 PlayStation 游戏，因为我拥有它们。"}, {"videoWebUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@kenziecourtney7/video/7581909204273745183", "submittedVideoUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@kenziecourtney7/video/7581909204273745183", "input": "https://www.ti